@DataBase
@WordWrap

@Node Main AppSize

					@{b}AppSize 1.1@{ub}


	AppSize is a small app-icon. It shows the size of files and directories and give you informations on the number of files and directories.

				@{" Installation - Usage " link Usage}
				@{"        Author        " link Auteur}

@Endnode

@Node Usage

					@{b}Installation@{ub}

	AppSize needs the reqtools.library and also OS 2.0 or greater.


                                            @{b}Usage@{ub}

	AppSize is an app-icon, so this is an icon on the WB screen... When you drop files on AppSize, their size are calculed and show in a reqtools requester.

@Endnode

